org.talend.core.model.metadata.builder.database.emf.connection
Interface DbConnectionType

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
DbConnectionTypeImpl
public interface DbConnectionType
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Db Connection Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Meta Data Table
  • Id
  • Label
  • Comment
  • Db Type
  • Driver Class
  • Url
  • Port
  • Username
  • Password
  • Schema
  • Sql Syntax
  • String Quote
  • Null Char

See Also:
DatabaseTalendPackage.getDbConnectionType()
